Base.ErrorVariableContents: Error bij uitlezen van telephonecentrale csv

Base.Explanation: Copy a variable from the session variable list. Both the name and value of the variable are copied. If the variable already exists in the project variable list, the value is overwritten.

ArrayElement.Name: Variable name
ArrayElement.Description: The name of the variable to be copied from the session variable list to the project variable list (example: %ConnectionString%).

Base.FunctionName: Replace substring: If name starts with substring (case insensitive)
Base.FunctionDescription: Replace the substring with the specified new substring if the name starts with the specified substring (case insensitive).

Data.TextValue: Er zijn één of meerdere passen gekoppeld aan gebruiker %samaccountName%, namelijk: %user_heeft_passen%.
